xvm version
xvm usage
xvm help

xvm init
xvm which [<pack>]
xvm status [local|global] [<pack>]
xvm remove

xvm set   [local|global] <pack> <version>|stable|latest
xvm unset [local|global] <pack>

xvm show <pack> [installed|available|stable|latest]
xvm pull <pack> <version>|stable|latest
xvm drop <pack> <version>|stable|latest

xvm show pack [installed|available]
xvm pull pack <name>
xvm drop pack <name>

xvm edit pack <name>
xvm push pack <name>
